microsim.space

Interface ObjectSpaceIterator<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>

    public interface ObjectSpaceIterator<E>
extends java.util.Iterator<E>
    A specific iterator for grids. For each value read it is possible to know what is its position on the grid with currentX() and currentY() methods.
